# Cursor rules for nativelink-mcp-server

- Use TypeScript (ESM) and keep source changes in `src/`.
- Add new tools under `src/tools/` and wire them in `src/index.ts`.
- Validate inputs with `zod` schemas colocated with the tool.
- Prefer small, composable helpers in `src/lib/`.
- Avoid introducing new runtime dependencies unless justified.
- Do not commit build output in `dist/`.
- Update `README.md` when adding tools or changing config.
